message.content:
∀ {G : ℝ → ℝ} (f : ℝ → ℝ) (hf : ∀ r : ℝ, G r = Inf {abs (r - sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)) | m n : ℤ}),
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ {G : ℝ → ℝ} (r : ℝ), (∀ (ε > 0), ∃ (M : ℝ), ∀ (m n : ℤ), |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)| < ε → r ≥ M) →
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ G : ℝ → ℝ, (∀ r > 0, G r = Inf {abs (r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)) | m n : ℤ}) → 
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → ∃ m n : ℤ, |r - (m^2 + 2 * n^2)^(1/2)| = 0 → Filter.Tendsto (fun r => G r) Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∃ G : ℝ → ℝ, (∀ r : ℝ, 0 < r → (∃ m n : ℤ, G r = |r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)|)) ∧ Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → ∃ (G : ℝ → ℝ), (∀ (m n : ℤ), 0 ≤ G r ∧ G r = abs (r - real.sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2))) ∧ Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → ∃ (G : ℝ → ℝ), (∀ m n : ℤ, G r = min (abs (r - sqrt (m^2 + 2*n^2)))) ∧ Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ (G : ℝ → ℝ), (∀ r > 0, G r = Inf {abs (r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)) | m n : ℤ}) → 
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
∀ {r : ℝ}, 0 < r → ∃ m n : ℤ, |r - Real.sqrt (m ^ 2 + 2 * n ^ 2)| ≤ G r ∧ Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)

∀ G : ℝ → ℝ, (∀ r : ℝ, 0 < r → ∃ (m n : ℤ), G r = abs (r - Real.sqrt (m^2 + 2 * n^2))) →
  Filter.Tendsto G Filter.atTop (nhds 0)
